bioghist.p:
John J. (Jack) Cronin born 1931, Cork, Ireland. Cockfield Brown agency: Copy chief and
        Creative Director circa 1960. JWT Montreal: Senior copywriter 1964; Creative Director 1966;
        Senior Vice President and Chief Executive Officer 1977. JWT Canada: Vice President 1967;
        Director 1972; Chief Operating Officer 1976. JWT Europe: Executive Vice President 1980. JWT
        corporate: Vice Chairman 1986; Chief Advertising Officer 1987.
